get_socv_repor...gma_multiplier(25.10)  get_socv_repor...gma_multiplier(25.10)

Name
       get_socv_reporting_nsigma_multiplier - Allows you to query sigma multi-
       plier setting for the specified view in setup or hold mode

Syntax
       get_socv_reporting_nsigma_multiplier

       [-help]

       -view <viewName>

       {[-setup | -hold ]}

       Allows  you to query sigma multiplier setting for the specified view in
       setup or hold mode.

Parameters
       -help  Prints out the command usage.

       -hold  Returns the sigma multiplier for hold mode.

       -setup Returns the sigma multiplier for setup mode.

       -view <viewName>
              Returns the sigma multiplier value for the specified view.

              Note: Applies to active views only.

Examples
              * The following command displays the  sigma  multiplier  setting
                for the specified view:

                innovus > set_socv_reporting_nsigma_multiplier -hold 2.5 -view
                default_emulate_view_hold

                innovus   >   get_socv_reporting_nsigma_multiplier  -view  de-
                fault_emulate_view_hold -hold

                2.500000

Related Information
